{"tid":1714750,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新華社：香港正處最危急關口","createTime":"2019-11-13T02:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T03:21:54.000Z","uid":56881,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"49995c09f59548a3b4ba6644f4aff4502e46e6e7","tid":1714750,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:42:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%96%B0%E8%8F%AF%E7%A4%BE-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%AD%A3%E8%99%95%E6%9C%80%E5%8D%B1%E6%80%A5%E9%97%9C%E5%8F%A3-232132607.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BE-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E8%2599%2595%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%258D%25B1%25E6%2580%25A5%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%258F%25A3-232132607.html&d=PzS6fk0mmUdoDXVWrKgE951QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=0fcd5359\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%96%B0%E8%8F%AF%E7%A4%BE-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%AD%A3%E8%99%95%E6%9C%80%E5%8D%B1%E6%80%A5%E9%97%9C%E5%8F%A3-232132607.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.G_qq4n61wpTalm0f2ArSQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/XINHUA-HK-191113-07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.G_qq4n61wpTalm0f2ArSQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FXINHUA-HK-191113-07.jpg&h=2184d07f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新華社：香港正處最危急關口<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】新華社時評指香港正處最危急關口。<br />\n<br />\n評論指修例風波至今已五個多月，暴徒暴力活動變本加厲，無法無天，惡行已與修例無關；暴力就是暴力，不僅絕不會達到所謂的民主自由，反而是對民主的褻瀆，對廣大港人人權、自由的侵犯。<br />\n<br />\n評論稱，反中亂港政客借機搞亂香港，把香港變成一個獨立或半獨立政治實體，假高度自治港人治港之名，行完全自治對抗中央之實，最終使一國兩制名存實亡。<br />\n<br />\n時評指香港正處最危急關口，許多港人被暴力裹挾進入一種分裂病態，只論情緒不講事實，只問觀點不分是非，如果任由這種不正常繼續發酵，留給社會自我修正的時間將所剩無幾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地既黑錢凍過水"},{"pid":"e24b1ecb